    {
      "instruction": "<p>Return the pan to a medium-high heat with a very generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>(enough to cover the whole base of the pan)</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>coated meat-free chick'n </strong>and cook for 6-7 min or until golden and warmed through – this is your <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>meat-free chick'n</strong></p><p>Tip: Add more oil to the pan if it is looking a little dry</p><p>Meanwhile, slice your <strong>red chilli[es] </strong>finely</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
