        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>salad</strong>, then pat it dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Fill your <strong>toasted brioche buns </strong>with a dollop of <strong>mayo</strong>, a <strong>roasted pepper half</strong>, the<strong> fiery Marmite-glazed meat-free chick'n</strong> and the <strong>salad</strong></p><p>Serve the<strong> chips</strong> to the side and garnish with the <strong>chilli rounds</strong> (can't handle the heat? Go easy!) – these are your<strong> chilli fries</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
